<HL>
   Saudis Trying to Get
   Foreigners Interested
   In Its Bond Market
   ----
   Special to The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
